   <body>
      <p>The Program Manager component provides the following capabilities:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Setting up program header including specifying program general information, formulas used to calculated qualifications and benefits, program schedule information, and payment information if applicable.</li>
         <li>Setting up program scope that includes filters to filter qualification and benefit lines.</li>
         <li>Adding products.</li>
         <li>Specifying benefit and benefit dates for products.</li>
         <li>Adding participants.</li>
         <li>Adding notes and attachment.</li>
         <li>Program Template. Also called Program Accelerator. Any program can function as a program accelerator. Using the cloning functionality, a user can clone a program, make updates on the cloned copy and save as a new program.  </li>
      </ul>
